data.description: Great single story home featuring 3 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. Home is clean and move in ready! Great farmhouse sink with concrete counters, backsplash & freshly painted cabinets. Newer microwave & water heater is only 1 year old.  Kitchen & bathrooms also have newer fixtures. New flooring in main areas. Both the front & back yard are a blank canvas for your landscaping ideas. The backyard makes a great space for entertaining. Great starter house, or for someone looking to downsize or an investor. Close to everything Fernley has to offer, close to USA Parkway & easy access from main street or US95A.  Come see this great house before its gone!
